@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api/skiDays
@lastCreatedId = {{lastCreatedId}}

### 1️⃣ Get all ski days
GET {{baseUrl}}
Content-Type: application/json


### 2️⃣ Create a new ski day
# @name createSkiDay
POST {{baseUrl}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "date": "2025-01-15",
  "location": "Park City",
  "runs": 12,
  "topSpeed": 49,
  "verticalFeet": 7200,
  "activityType": "Skiing",
  "notes": "Sunny morning, icy later in the day."
}

### 3️⃣ Save the created ski day's ID for later requests
@lastCreatedId = {{createSkiDay.response.body._id}}


### 4️⃣ Get that newly created ski day
GET {{baseUrl}}/{{lastCreatedId}}
Content-Type: application/json


### 5️⃣ Update the ski day
PUT {{baseUrl}}/{{lastCreatedId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "runs": 15,
  "notes": "Updated: added a few more afternoon runs."
}


### 6️⃣ Delete the ski day
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/{{lastCreatedId}}
Content-Type: application/json
